00055 void CHPMultiDataFileReaderTest::testReadCN()
00056 {
00057         affymetrix_calvin_data::ProbeSetMultiDataCopyNumberData e;
00058         ParameterNameValueType param;
00059         CHPMultiDataData data2;
00060         CHPMultiDataFileReader reader;
00061         reader.SetFilename("../data/CHP_MultiData_file_cn");
00062         reader.Read(data2);
00063 
00064         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetAlgName() == L"sig");
00065         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetAlgVersion() == L"1.0");
00066         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetArrayType() == L"test3");
00067         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetEntryCount(CopyNumberMultiDataType) == 2);
00068         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetEntryCount(GenotypeMultiDataType) == 0);
00069         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetEntryCount(ExpressionMultiDataType) == 0);
00070 
00071         ParameterNameValueTypeList p = data2.GetAlgParams();
00072         ParameterNameValueTypeList::iterator it = p.begin();
00073         param = *it;
00074         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetName() == L"an1");
00075         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetValueText() == L"av1");
00076 
00077         p = data2.GetSummaryParams();
00078         it = p.begin();
00079         param = *it;
00080         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetName() == L"sn1");
00081         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetValueText() == L"sv1");
00082 
00083     data2.GetCopyNumberEntry(CopyNumberMultiDataType, 0, e);
00084         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.chr == 10);
00085         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.position == 11);
00086         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.name == "abc");
00087         data2.GetCopyNumberEntry(CopyNumberMultiDataType, 1, e);
00088         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.chr == 20);
00089         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.position == 21);
00090         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.name == "xyz");
00091 }

00121         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetValueText() == L"sv1");
00122 
00123     data2.GetCopyNumberVariationEntry(CopyNumberVariationMultiDataType, 0, e);

00135 void CHPMultiDataFileReaderTest::testRead()
00136 {
00137     affymetrix_calvin_data::ProbeSetMultiDataExpressionData ex;
00138     affymetrix_calvin_data::ProbeSetMultiDataGenotypeData gn;
00139         ParameterNameValueType param;
00140 
00141         CHPMultiDataData data2;
00142         CHPMultiDataFileReader reader;
00143         reader.SetFilename("../data/CHP_MultiData_file");
00144         reader.Read(data2);
00145 
00146         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetAlgName() == L"sig");
00147         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetAlgVersion() == L"1.0");
00148         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetArrayType() == L"test3");
00149         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetEntryCount(ExpressionMultiDataType) == 1);
00150         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetEntryCount(GenotypeMultiDataType) == 2);
00151 
00152     // expression
00153     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetNumMetricColumns(ExpressionMultiDataType) == 0);
00154     data2.GetExpressionEntry(ExpressionMultiDataType, 0, ex);
00155         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(ex.quantification, 10.0f, 0.0001f);
00156         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(ex.name == "ex1");
00157 
00158     // genotype
00159     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetNumMetricColumns(GenotypeMultiDataType) == 2);
00160     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetMetricColumnName(GenotypeMultiDataType, 0) == L"int");
00161     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetMetricColumnName(GenotypeMultiDataType, 1) == L"float");
00162 
00163     data2.GetGenotypeEntry(GenotypeMultiDataType, 0, gn);
00164         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gn.call == 1);
00165         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(gn.confidence, 11.0f, 0.0001f);
00166         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gn.name == "gn1");
00167     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gn.metrics.size() == 2);
00168     param = gn.metrics[0];
00169     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetParameterType() == ParameterNameValueType::Int32Type);
00170     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetValueInt32() == 1);
00171     param = gn.metrics[1];
00172     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetParameterType() == ParameterNameValueType::FloatType);
00173     CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(param.GetValueFloat(), 2.0f, 0.00001f);
00174 
00175     data2.GetGenotypeEntry(GenotypeMultiDataType, 1, gn);
00176         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gn.call == 2);
00177         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(gn.confidence, 22.0f, 0.0001f);
00178         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gn.name == "gn2");
00179     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gn.metrics.size() == 2);
00180     param = gn.metrics[0];
00181     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetParameterType() == ParameterNameValueType::Int32Type);
00182     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetValueInt32() == 2);
00183     param = gn.metrics[1];
00184     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetParameterType() == ParameterNameValueType::FloatType);
00185     CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(param.GetValueFloat(), 3.0f, 0.00001f);
00186 }
